ZH: 我们应该抵制任何形式的歧视。
EN: We should resist any form of discrimination.

ZH: 他们呼吁市民抵制不健康的食品。
EN: They called on the citizens to resist unhealthy food.

ZH: 抵制侵犯人权的行为是每个人的责任。
EN: Resisting human rights violations is everyone's responsibility.

