EN: Their movement calls on everyone to resist any form of personal attack.

ZH: 抵制言论暴力是每个人的责任。
EN: Resisting speech violence is everyone's responsibility.

ZH: 这次活动旨在抵制家庭暴力。
EN: This event aims to resist domestic violence.

